data.description: Immaculate 4BR, 2BA ranch style home located on a spacious, fully fenced 0.21 acre corner lot in the quest established neighborhood of Pikes Peak Park. Fabulous mountain views! Level, low maintenance landscaping w/mature trees. Central air, heat, & humidifier for year round comfort. Hardwood floors & newer vinyl windows throughout most of the ML. The Entry offers a coat closet & leads into the Living Rm that provides a large front window which brings in abundant natural light, & a wood burning fireplace w/brick surround to cozy up to on chilly winter nights. The Living Rm opens into the Eat-In Kitchen that features a tile floor, a counter bar, & oak cabinets w/ beautiful granite countertops. Appl incl a smooth top range oven, built in microwave, dishwasher, & SS side by side refrigerator. There are 2BRs w/hardwood floors & a Full Bathroom w/vanity, mirror, & tub/shower on the ML. The Finished Basement has a spacious, versatile Family Rm w/neutral carpet, great for entertaining family & friends. There are 2BRs w/neutral carpet & a Shower Bathroom, great for guests, in-laws, or teens. The Utility Rm offers upper cabinets, a folding table, freezer, & washer & dryer w/pedestals that stay. The huge fenced backyard offers a concrete patio, fire pit, storage shed for tools & toys, & a 2-car detached garage w/an extra wide driveway for small boat or RV parking, Ideal location close to schools, park, & entertainment. Easy commute to Ft Carson & Peterson Space Force Base. Min to I-25.
